<h2><strong>CADmeister2020Version Upgrade (CAM)</strong></h2><h3><strong>&bull; CAM &bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>1.&nbsp;Machining Order Optimization /Tool Life Division</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Traditional NC data splitting operations and challenges</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_1.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;Machining Order Optimization &amp; Tool Life Division</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_1.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>2.&nbsp;Automatic Curved Machining Design Enhancements</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>The machining range and process set can be automatically determined according to the surface color and bulk calculations can be performed.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_2.1.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_2.1.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;Design Curved Srf Machining Automatically Effect</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_2.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>3.&nbsp;Scan Machining Process</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Improved special shape tool support and pick feed type</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;CAM-DX&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>4.&nbsp;Path Calculation Engine</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Strengthen the support for special shaped tools and corner machining</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_4.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;CAM-ADVANCE&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>5.&nbsp;Comparison of cutting lengths</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Since the pitch can be made larger than a ball tool, the cutting length (machining time) can be shortened</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_5.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;CAM-PRF&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>6.&nbsp;Deep Engraving Layer Division</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Automatic machining design has been developing</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_6.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>7.&nbsp;Automatic avoid approach and retraction interference</strong></h4><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_7.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;CAM-ATTRIBUTE&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>8.&nbsp;Cross Hole Deceleration</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Cross Hole Deceleration Support</p><p>&nbsp; &gt; Available to control the decelerate cutting feed speed at the intersection hole machining.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_8.1.3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &gt; It is now possible to automatically create machining data considering the machining order of intersecting holes.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_8.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;Drilling Process Improvement</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt; Straight-line Interpolation (G01) enables deceleration at hole intersections</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_8.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;CAM Attribute Integration</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt; It is a function that automatically recognizes hole shape and automatically creates drilling data.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_8.3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;BASE&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>9.&nbsp;Machined Surface Color Feature Conversion Efficiency Improvement</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Attribute conversion time from color has been greatly improved by machining surface color feature conversion</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_9.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;Reduces processing time in attribute conversion regardless of the number of member surfaces or attribute surfaces</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_9.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;CAM-STRUCTURE&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>10.&nbsp;Supports Pond and Island for Seat Machining</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>It is now possible to generate a path for seat surface that recognizes ponds and islands</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_10.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;Efficient machining data can now be created without shape correction</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAM/CADmeister2020_CAM_10.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h2>&nbsp;</h2>